[options="header",cols="10%,10%,10%,70%"]
|======

| Property
| Mandatory 
| Type
| Description


| action
| yes
| string
| Action of the cause. A event can for example be cause by a delete action.

| type
| no
| string
| Type of the element that is referenced by the cause.

| uuid
| no
| string
| Uuid of the element that is referenced by the cause.

